HEADWORD: Iranian
<hw>I*ra"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
Iran.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A native of Iran; also, the
Iranian or Persian language, a division of the Aryan family of
languages, the modern version of which is called
